_sText:
In this map you can find some riddles and two very hot specials on the top of the two buildings. There are a scorpion and a catapult which shoot you to the other top :D. There is a riddleroom and a secret place where you have to type a code to get the awp.  Hope you enjoy playing the map and flying over the heads of the other players :D. 
Thx for playing 
Yours, Shockwave)))

P.S. The Code for the AWP is 463 just for them which download my map and find the place :D
